	<div class="commentBody">	
		<div id="comment_body_4068119">It's good that someone such as yourself advocates trying everything that might even be in the right direction.<br>I'm new to programming but I'm making headway. I'm new to my OS (FreeBSD) but I keep poking, keep googling, keep playing with the ports. I don't know what I'm doing, exactly, but every mistake I make teaches me something. Usually there'll be a clue, a bit of rope that I can use to pull myself to the next problem.<br> <br></div>
	</div>

